NK039(ti)033:1: // kri p+aa nu ko bi d+aa ra k+aa ma tu
NK039(ti)033:2: pa t+ai ba dz+ra d+h+aa tu sh+w+aa ri s+ya bi
NK039(ti)033:3: dza ha ra /// 'dod khams bdag mo rdo rje
NK039(ti)033:4: dbyings phyug ma'i smin byed yongs 'du'i sa brtol bzhugs
NK039(ti)033:5: dza ha ra /// so // dus gsum rgyal ba'i bstan bsrung ma //
NK039(ti)033:6: dpal ldan yum chen la btud nas //
NK039(ti)033:7: gang de'i smin byed bdud rtsi'i mtsho //
NK039(ti)033:8: ngo mtshar grub pa'i gzhung bzhin spel //
NK039(ti)033:9: 'dir slob dpon chen po d+ha na sang kri ta dang //
NK039(ti)033:10: pad+ma'i bka' srol ltar lha mo rang byung rgyal mo'i dbang bskur gyi cho ga la gsum /
NK039(ti)033:11: sbyor ba dngos gzhi rjes so //
NK039(ti)033:12: dang po la cho gar mi gtogs pa'i sbyor ba dang /
NK039(ti)033:13: cho gar gtogs pa'i sbyor ba'o //
NK039(ti)033:15: dben la yid dang mthun pa'i gnas su stegs bde ba la /
NK039(ti)033:16: dkyil 'khor ni ma mo byang chub sems rgyud las /
NK039(ti)033:17: mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK039(ti)033:18: zla gam dbang chen 'bar ba'i man+dala //
NK039(ti)033:19: gru chad gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK039(ti)033:20: de rgyab thod phreng rdo rje'i rwa ba me dpung 'bar //
NK039(ti)033:22: dbus su gru gsum mthing nag /
NK039(ti)033:23: de'i logs gsum zla gam la khrag mtsho dmar po /
NK039(ti)033:24: de rgyab thod pa'i rwa ba gur khang /
NK039(ti)033:25: de rgyab gru chad thod pas kha bad byas /
NK039(ti)033:26: de rgyab khrag mtsho dmar po 'jigs su rung ba /
NK039(ti)033:27: sgo rdzogs rta bab bzhi pa /
NK039(ti)033:28: dur khrod rdo rwa me ri dang bcas pa /
NK039(ti)033:29: dbus su gri gug thod khrag dang thig le dmar /
NK039(ti)033:30: gru gsum zla gam ngos kyi gtso mo'i mdun na gsum /
NK039(ti)033:31: g.yas g.yon du gnyis re rnams dang zur gsum du thig le nag /
NK039(ti)033:32: gru chad gri gug thod khrag brgyad /
NK039(ti)033:33: khrag khyam la thig le smug po rnams bkod pa bris pa'i ras bris sam /
NK039(ti)033:36: ka p+aa la'i nang dbang gi dmar gtor snying gzugs
NK039(ti)033:37: ma gru gang ba gcig zas sna dang chang phud
NK039(ti)033:38: kyis bran pa / sku tsaka dang gtor gdugs me
NK039(ti)033:39: ri rgyan bzang pos brgyan cing 'khor lha grangs gtor
NK039(ti)033:40: kyis bran pa / chung ngam / b+ha ling gis mtshan pa dang /
NK039(ti)033:41: mdun du rten gtor bshams de mthar sman rag sogs mchod pas bskor /
NK039(ti)033:42: a mri ta'i rdzas kyis gang ba'i ka p+aa la
NK039(ti)033:43: sin+du ra'i me long chos 'byung gi dbus su ma
NK039(ti)033:44: b+h+yohmatshana pas bkab pa mdun du bzhag /
NK039(ti)033:48: spro na zan ling sogs sgra la chas /
NK039(ti)033:52: 'bul gtor rnga rol sogs tshogs par bya'o //
NK039(ti)033:54: rdo rje gzhon nu'i dag gi rnal 'byor bzlas pa dang bsdu ldang gi mthar /
NK039(ti)033:55: sngon du slob dpon rang nyid kyis mdun bskyed la
NK039(ti)033:56: dmigs mchod gsol bsnyen pa dang bcas pa rgyas par
NK039(ti)033:57: grub 'phral / b+han+d+ha'i nang du ye shes kyi dpal
NK039(ti)033:58: lha mo bong drel med pa gcig gsal nas bsnyen
NK039(ti)033:59: pa cung zad byas pa mthar 'od zhu bya /
NK039(ti)033:60: slob ma'i las bya ba'i ched du 'khrugs bskang byas nas /
NK039(ti)033:61: las bum du bgegs mthar byed sgyu 'phrul 'byung ba ltar bsgrub /
NK039(ti)033:62: gnyis la'ang thun min dang thun mong gi dmigs rim bya tshul lo //
NK039(ti)033:64: don du gnyer ba'i dad ldan dam tshig thub ngos rnams la khrus dang /
NK039(ti)033:65: phyag gi gral du 'khod bcug ste /
NK039(ti)033:67: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad rnam
NK039(ti)033:68: mkhyen bla na med pa sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang
NK039(ti)033:69: thob par bya / de yi ched du bstan pa
NK039(ti)033:70: srung ba'i chos skyong gi smin byed zhu snyam pa'i
NK039(ti)033:71: thugs bskyed pa rin po che gsal btab nas gsan
NK039(ti)033:72: thob par bya / par zhu / de yang yon tan rin po che 'phags pa sdud pa las /
NK039(ti)033:73: rin chen chos kyang dkon la rtag tu tshe ba'ang mang /
NK039(ti)033:74: de la bar chad bya phyir bdud ni spro bar 'gyur /
NK039(ti)033:75: zhes gsungs pa ltar spyi dam pa'i chos sgrub pa'i
NK039(ti)033:76: gang zag la bar chad kyi 'tshe ba mang zhing
NK039(ti)033:77: / khyad par du'ang bdud dang nag po'i phyogs thams
NK039(ti)033:78: cad kyis sdang ba'i glags tshol ba mang bas de
NK039(ti)033:79: / 'dul ba'i phyir / rgyal ba thabs mkhas la
NK039(ti)033:80: thugs rje'i dbang phyug chen po de nyid kyis rgyud
NK039(ti)033:81: dang man ngag gi tshul du /
NK039(ti)033:82: bar chad sel zhing gdug pa 'dul ba'i bstan bsrung du ma zhig bstan pa /
NK039(ti)033:83: gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir rdo rje theg pa gsar rnying bka' srol rnams su /
NK039(ti)033:84: ye shes dang 'jig rten gyi rang bzhin pho mo'i
NK039(ti)033:85: rgyud du gtogs pa'i bstan srung mi 'dra ba du
NK039(ti)033:87: skabs su bab pa rje btsun bla ma 'jam pa'i
NK039(ti)033:88: dbyangs shar kahthoga pa chen po bla chen spobs pa
NK039(ti)033:89: mtha' yas zhes snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i bskyed
NK039(ti)033:90: rdzogs rdzogs pa chen po'i bstan pa'i bdag por gzhugs
NK039(ti)033:91: shing phrin las nam mkha' dang mnyam pa de'i snyan
NK039(ti)033:92: brgyud man ngag gi chos bskor las byung ba rdo
NK039(ti)033:93: rje'i chos skyong ba'i bsrung ma dpal nag po lcam
NK039(ti)033:94: dral rnam gsum nas snying nye la mthu byin che
NK039(ti)033:95: ba / 'grub sla la bkra shis pa ste thun mong dang /
NK039(ti)033:96: bla ma ltar bsten pas ye shes 'char /
NK039(ti)033:97: yi dam ltar bsten pas dngos grub stsol ba /
NK039(ti)033:98: tshe 'di phyi bar gsum gyi legs nyes skyong nges pa ste /
NK039(ti)033:99: mchog gi khyad par gsum dang ldan pa rgyud kyi khungs che ba /
NK039(ti)033:100: man ngag gi phyag len zhib pa /
NK039(ti)033:101: nus mthu rno ngar gyi gnad tshangs ba /
NK039(ti)033:102: gru thob kyi lugs bzang po khyad par du 'phags pa bzhugs pa las /
NK039(ti)033:103: bye brag 'dir spyi rgyud srid pa ma mo'i dems chen mo sogs las zin cing /
NK039(ti)033:104: sgos rgyud mkha' 'gro ma mo lce 'bar ma dang /
NK039(ti)033:105: ma mo byang chub sems kyi rgyud dang /
NK039(ti)033:106: rdo rje lha mo nag mo dbang phyug ma'i rgyud dang /
NK039(ti)033:107: 'phags pa dpal ldan lha mo nag po'i sngags rgyud
NK039(ti)033:108: sogs kyis bstan don thugs kyi ma mo rang byung
NK039(ti)033:109: rgyal mo re ti bran g.yog gi dbang bskur dang
NK039(ti)033:110: rjes gnang bsgrub par bgyi ba /
NK039(ti)033:112: de yang don la rgyal ba thams cad kyi yum
NK039(ti)033:113: shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin ma'am kun tu
NK039(ti)033:114: bzang mo dang / rdo rje rnal 'byor mar grags
NK039(ti)033:115: pa nyid mtshan dang sku yi bkod pa tsam las
NK039(ti)033:117: chos thams cad skye med ma mo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo sangs rgyas dang /
NK039(ti)033:118: de ma rtogs pa'i gdul bya la phrin las drag
NK039(ti)033:119: pos 'dul ba'i bcom ldan 'das bla med he ru
NK039(ti)033:120: ka'i nyid bzhi mu kha le dang dbyer ma mchis
NK039(ti)033:122: thun mong gdul bya'i tshur mthong la /
NK039(ti)033:123: las tshul bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i thabs mkhas kyi mdzad pa cir yang 'char bas /
NK039(ti)033:124: sngon ri rab kyi rtse mo sum cu rtsa gsum
NK039(ti)033:125: lha yi dga' tshal du yab dbang phyug chen po
NK039(ti)033:126: dang yum u ma dka' bzlog lha mo'i sras mor
NK039(ti)033:127: 'khrungs te lha ma yin gyi dmag dpung tshar btsad
NK039(ti)033:128: / dka' thub kyi tshal bsten pas lha mo dung skyong ma'am /
NK039(ti)033:129: ri khrod lo ma gyon par grags /
NK039(ti)033:130: las dbang gis srin po d+ha sha g+h+ri wa'i g.yo thabs la brten nas chung mar khyer ba /
NK039(ti)033:131: khyo shi bas srin po'i ral gri sogs khyer te 'bros pas lceb cing /
NK039(ti)033:132: smon lam mthus chos rgyal gshin rje'i sring mor gyur nas /
NK039(ti)033:133: khol mo re ma ti'am skem ma chu srin gdong dang bcas /
NK039(ti)033:134: rdzu 'phrul gyi bong drel la bcibs nas phyogs bcur
NK039(ti)033:135: rgyu zhing sems can la gnod tshe'i tshul sogs kyang
NK039(ti)033:137: bram ze mchog sred kyi grogs su byas te sgrub thabs bstan /
NK039(ti)033:138: byang chub shing gi drung du phyin te yang dag
NK039(ti)033:139: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ston mchog thugs rje can
NK039(ti)033:140: las sems bskyed de srog gi snying po 'bul /
NK039(ti)033:141: khro rgyal rta mgrin gyi gsang ba'i gzungs ma bgyis /
NK039(ti)033:142: dpal phyag na rdo rje las dam mnos te sa brgyad sa'i sems mar gyur /
NK039(ti)033:143: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bstan pa bsrung ba'i gtso mo /
NK039(ti)033:144: ye shes kyi mgon po rnams kyi yum dang lcam
NK039(ti)033:145: sogs cir yang ston pas bzhugs pa 'di nyid kyi
NK039(ti)033:146: sgrub thabs la rje na ro pa'i bka' srol dud
NK039(ti)033:147: sol ma dang / pan chen dmar mo'i lugs kyis
NK039(ti)033:148: dmag zor ma sogs gsar ma'i sde rnams kyang 'di
NK039(ti)033:150: ma mo thams cad kyi rgyud lung man ngag rnams
NK039(ti)033:151: grub pa'i slob dpon brgyad kyi nang tshan d+ha na
NK039(ti)033:152: sam kri ta la bka' bab pa las 'dir der
NK039(ti)033:153: o rgyan dus gsum mkhyen pa la gnang ba dang
NK039(ti)033:154: / des thugs sras rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga'i
NK039(ti)033:155: nang tshan ma mo bran khol 'brog mi dpal gyi
NK039(ti)033:156: ye shes la gnang ba nas bzung /
NK039(ti)033:157: so zur gnub gsum sogs gsang chen rnying ma'i rig
NK039(ti)033:158: 'dzin gsang sngags kyi rgyal po gong ma thams cad
NK039(ti)033:159: kyis bka' srung du bsten pa dpal rang byung rgyal
NK039(ti)033:160: mo dang / yang slob dpon d+ha na sam kri
NK039(ti)033:161: las bee ro tsa nas gsan cing de las 'brog
NK039(ti)033:162: mo dang / mi dpal seng / de las rim
NK039(ti)033:163: bzhin brgyud pa bla ma dpal 'dzin chen po las
NK039(ti)033:164: shar kahthoga pas gsan pa'i ma mo rang byung rgyal
NK039(ti)033:166: yang slob dpon pad+mas mdzad pa'i gzhung lcags phur bdun pa'am /
NK039(ti)033:167: ma mo srog sgrub tu grags pa'i skor su hring
NK039(ti)033:168: ba zhang btsun dar ma rin chen gyis gter nas
NK039(ti)033:169: bton pa / zhang btsun pa'i slob ma bla ma
NK039(ti)033:170: brag stod kyi cog ro ga chu ba chen po
NK039(ti)033:171: las gsan pa bcas bka' gter gsum chu bo gcig
NK039(ti)033:172: 'dres su gyur pa'i ye shes pa ltar dbang bskur
NK039(ti)033:173: bton pa / ba dang / 'jig rten pa ltar
NK039(ti)033:174: las kyii rjes su gnang ba gnyis 'bul ba'i dang
NK039(ti)033:175: po la'ang slob dpon gyi bgyi bar 'os pa grub
NK039(ti)033:176: pa sku nyid kyis bgyi bar 'os pa spyor ba
NK039(ti)033:177: dbang gi snod sgrub pa dang /
NK039(ti)033:178: dngos gzhi dbang bskur sbyin pa gnyis kyi dang po
NK039(ti)033:179: bla ma la dbang bskur zhu ba'i yon du man+dala
NK039(ti)033:180: 'bul bar zhu / zhes mtshams sbyar nas man+dala 'bul du bzhugs /
NK039(ti)033:181: gsol ba gdab pa 'di yi rjes zlos zhu /
NK039(ti)033:182: sh+aakya seng ge'i bstan pa la //
NK039(ti)033:183: byang chub tu ni sems bskyed nas //
NK039(ti)033:184: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)033:185: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo yi //
NK039(ti)033:186: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub dang //
NK039(ti)033:187: dbang dang phrin las rtsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)033:189: mdun gyi nam mkhar bla ma bla med he ru
NK039(ti)033:190: ka yum dang bcas pa'i skur gsal ba la rgyal
NK039(ti)033:191: ba sras dang bcas pas bskor ba mngon sum bzhin
NK039(ti)033:192: du bzhugs pa'i spyan sngar skyabs su 'gro ba dang
NK039(ti)033:193: / chos thams cad rang bzhin dag pa'i chos sku
NK039(ti)033:194: yin pa la ngo ma shes shing 'khor bar 'khyams
NK039(ti)033:195: pa'i sems can thams cad sangs rgyas la 'god par
NK039(ti)033:196: bya ba'i ched du sems bskyed de tshogs bsags pa
NK039(ti)033:197: / la / rgyun bshags yan lag brgyad pa bya
NK039(ti)033:198: ba 'di yi tshig rjes su don dran pas rjes
NK039(ti)033:199: / la / zlos zhu / rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal sogs lan gsum /
NK039(ti)033:200: tshogs zhing de dag gi spyan sngar gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i spyi dang bre brag gi /
NK039(ti)033:201: bsdus pa rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig
NK039(ti)033:202: thams cad 'dzin par bagyi'o snyams pas 'di'i rjes zlos
NK039(ti)033:203: shig // bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK039(ti)033:204: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK039(ti)033:205: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //
NK039(ti)033:206: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK039(ti)033:207: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK039(ti)033:208: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK039(ti)033:209: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK039(ti)033:210: rdo rje rgyal pos byin rlabs mdzod //
NK039(ti)033:212: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrub //
NK039(ti)033:213: byang chub spyod dka' bdag gis bskyed //
NK039(ti)033:215: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK039(ti)033:217: da ye shes ma mo snying zhugs kyi dbang gi
NK039(ti)033:218: gzhi dang po dgod cing ye shes dbab pa la
NK039(ti)033:220: khyed rang rnams kyi lus 'od kyi rang bzhin du
NK039(ti)033:221: gyur pa'i snying ga'i nang du skad cig gis sprul
NK039(ti)033:222: pa'i dre'u smug po rlung gi gshogs pa can /
NK039(ti)033:223: rkang gsum myur mgyog rdzu 'phrul gyi rtsal dang ldan pa /
NK039(ti)033:224: thod skam 'bar ba dang bswe sga dmar po sbrul nag gi gong smed can /
NK039(ti)033:226: byi ru dang rin po che'i srab dang /
NK039(ti)033:227: mi mgo skom po stong pa'i dam las 'phyang ba'i dril bu g.yer kha'i d+r+wa bas brgyan pa'i steng /
NK039(ti)033:228: dpal ldan lha mo sku mdog mthing nag tu 'dug pa /
NK039(ti)033:230: rab tu khro pa'i zhal gcig spyan gsum bgrad cing
NK039(ti)033:231: mche ba bzhi rnam par gtsigs nas ljags glog ltar
NK039(ti)033:232: 'dril ba / 'gyur ba'i khro gnyer bskyod cing smin
NK039(ti)033:233: tshugs dus rlung gi bsdus pa'i char sprin ltar gnag
NK039(ti)033:234: 'dril ba / pa bsdud pa / ral pa khoms
NK039(ti)033:235: nag gyen du bardzesa shing mthur du bshal ba'i thod
NK039(ti)033:236: pa bcu drug gi rtsa chings dang /
NK039(ti)033:237: thod skam lngas dbu brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)033:238: ral gri rno gdug 'bar ba'i sdigs pa'i yu ba can phyag g.yas na 'dzin cing /
NK039(ti)033:239: srin khrag bcud kyis gang ba'i thod phor g.yon na 'dzin pa /
NK039(ti)033:240: sbrul dang rus chas stag lpags glang ko re lde gsol zhing zhing gi phra kheb g.yo ba /
NK039(ti)033:241: rma bya'i mdongs sgro dbu la mdzes shing snyan cha seng sbrul 'dogs pa /
NK039(ti)033:242: dpral bar zla ba tshes shing /
NK039(ti)033:244: 'ja' tshon mtha' skud btab pa'i dar nag gi go
NK039(ti)033:245: zu bcing bar lam ste gyur pa'i mos pa mdzod
NK039(ti)033:246: / de yi gnas gsum du dkar zla ba /
NK039(ti)033:248: h'u mthing nyi ma la gnas pa'o //
NK039(ti)033:249: de ni dam tshig sems dpa' dang ting 'dzin sems
NK039(ti)033:250: dpa'i thugs kar pad+ma nyi ma'i gdan steng na mahdang
NK039(ti)033:251: b+h+yohmathinga ka 'od zer 'bar ba zhig bsgom nas bla
NK039(ti)033:252: ma la dpal rdo rje gzhon nu dngos yin snyams
NK039(ti)033:253: pa'i 'du shes kyis rjes zlos zhu /
NK039(ti)033:254: bla ma rin po che bdag la dpal ldan lha mo dbab par mdzad du gsol /
NK039(ti)033:255: yum chen ma chen dbab par mdzad du gsol /
NK039(ti)033:257: gsol ba btab pas slob dpon rdo rje gzhon nu'i
NK039(ti)033:258: thugs ka nas khro bo 'dod rgyal zhal gcig phyag
NK039(ti)033:259: gnyis lcags kyu dang phur pa thogs pa spros /
NK039(ti)033:260: phyag g.yas lcags kyu'i byang shar mtshams nas ye shes
NK039(ti)033:261: sems dpa' dpal ldan lha mo nag mo'i drel sna
NK039(ti)033:262: nas bzung / phyag g.yon gyi phur pas phyir 'brang
NK039(ti)033:263: gi bgegs bskrad de mdun du spyan drangs pa'i ye
NK039(ti)033:264: shes pa snying gi dbus su zhugs /
NK039(ti)033:265: dam tshig sems dpa' dang dbyer med du gyur par bsgom shig /
NK039(ti)033:266: ces bskul spos bsregs rol mor bcas /
NK039(ti)033:268: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)033:269: dad pa dang ni sogs mchod phrin 'bring po las byung ba'i tshig gis spyan 'dren mthar /
NK039(ti)033:270: ru ru ro ru tsa pa la a shug+me h'u b+h+yo dza dzah zhes bdun nam nyer gcig brjod /
NK039(ti)033:271: yang spog pa'i cho ga bya ba la dmigs pa
NK039(ti)033:272: 'di bzhin du mdzod khyad par rang rnams kyi snying
NK039(ti)033:273: khar bzhugs pa'i lha mo drel dang bcas pa'i zhabs
NK039(ti)033:274: su yam dz+him las rlung gi dkyil 'khor kha dog
NK039(ti)033:275: ljang gu / dbyibs gzhu brdung ba lta bu /
NK039(ti)033:276: zur bzhir ba dan g.yo bas mtshan pa'i ba dan
NK039(ti)033:277: bskyod rlung gis lha mo dang khyed rnams kyi lus
NK039(ti)033:278: bcas btegs nam mkha' la lam lam 'phyo /
NK039(ti)033:279: lha mo'i sku las bdud rtsiis char babs /
NK039(ti)033:280: rang gi lus thams cad gang /
NK039(ti)033:281: bde ba chen po bzod du med pa 'bar slar yang lha mo'i sku mang du byung /
NK039(ti)033:284: bla ma lha mo dbyer med pa rang sems stong nyid las bde ba 'bar bar bsam /
NK039(ti)033:285: nas gong gi sngags kyi mthar /
NK039(ti)033:286: be sha ya dz+heem a ah zhes btang ba drag tu brjod spos rol bya /
NK039(ti)033:287: yang ma mo'i thugs ka'i ma b+h+yohls 'od zer gyen du phros /
NK039(ti)033:288: sna bug g.yon nas tshur byung bas phyogs bcu nas rdo rje rnal 'byor ma dang /
NK039(ti)033:289: ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro thams cad ma mo nag
NK039(ti)033:290: mo'i rnam par spyan drangs snying gi ma mo la
NK039(ti)033:292: badz+ra d+aak+ka dak+ki ni b+ha ra hi bam ha ri
NK039(ti)033:293: ni sa ma mo nag mo ting lam ma mo
NK039(ti)033:294: nag mo dun ting b+h+yohdza h'u bam hoh zhes mang
NK039(ti)033:295: du bzlas shing spos rol bya /
NK039(ti)033:296: yang slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od dang ma mo'i
NK039(ti)033:297: thugs ka'i 'od zer lcags kyu lta bus snang srid
NK039(ti)033:298: ma mo thams cad kyi srog snying ma b+h+yoh'i yi
NK039(ti)033:299: ger drangs te khyed rang rnams kyi snying gi ma
NK039(ti)033:301: nas b+h+yo bdun ma dgu ma'i sngags /
NK039(ti)033:306: dza dza dzah zhes spos rol bya /
NK039(ti)033:308: ye shes pa bstan par gyur cig /
NK039(ti)033:309: ces rdo rje spyi bor bkod /
NK039(ti)033:310: de yang mdun 'dir chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid
NK039(ti)033:311: kyi ye shes kyi rang rtsal dur khrod chen po
NK039(ti)033:312: 'jigs su rung ba thod skam gyi gzhal med khang
NK039(ti)033:313: gi gru gsum gyi dbus su dpal ldan lha mo
NK039(ti)033:314: chen mo / mdun du chu srin gdong can /
NK039(ti)033:315: zla gam khrag mtsho gsum gyi mdun du gsum /
NK039(ti)033:316: g.yas g.yon gnyis re'i ma bdun zur gsum ma gsum /
NK039(ti)033:317: gru chad kyi stod bzhir sring mo bzhi /
NK039(ti)033:319: khyams la dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad de rtsa ba'i lha bzhi bcu zhe brgyad /
NK039(ti)033:320: yan lag gi lha mo stong /
NK039(ti)033:321: bdud mo bye ba'i tshogs rnams dang bcas te /
NK039(ti)033:322: dpal lha mo'i thugs ye shes kho na'i rnam par
NK039(ti)033:323: 'phrul pa las 'char ba rten brten par bcas pa
NK039(ti)033:324: mngon sum na mthong bar mos pa de dag sbyor
NK039(ti)033:325: ba dbang gi snod du bsgrub pa'o //
NK039(ti)033:326: gnyis pa dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi dbang lnga po /
NK039(ti)033:327: rdzas la brten nas dbang gi tshul du bskur ba dang /
NK039(ti)033:328: gtor ma la brten nas byin rlabs kyi tshul du bskur ba'o //
NK039(ti)033:330: gsol ba 'debs pa 'di'i rjes su zlos shig /
NK039(ti)033:331: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo bla
NK039(ti)033:332: ma rin po che bdag la dpal ldan lha mo'i
NK039(ti)033:333: sku'i dbang bskur du gsol zhes gsol ba btab pa
NK039(ti)033:334: la / thod bum gzhal med khang gi nang du
NK039(ti)033:335: ye shes kyi ma mo zhu ba'i shes rab kyi
NK039(ti)033:336: pha rol du phyin ma'i ye shes bdud rtsis khrus
NK039(ti)033:337: byas shing ngag lam du bstims te dbang bskur bas
NK039(ti)033:338: lha mo'i sku yi dbang bskur ba thob ste rang
NK039(ti)033:339: gi lus lha mo'i skur gyur /
NK039(ti)033:340: lus phung khams kyi dri ma thams cad dag par mos /
NK039(ti)033:341: srid gsum b+hany+dza'i bzang khang du /
NK039(ti)033:342: dus gsum rnam rtog sel ba yi //
NK039(ti)033:343: ye shes bdud rtsi dri med pas //
NK039(ti)033:344: bde ba chen por dbang bskur ro //
NK039(ti)033:345: sarba ta th+aa ga ta prany+dz+aa p+aa ra mi ta ma mahka ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK039(ti)033:346: zhes rdo rje'i rtses bdud rtsi'i chu gtor spyi bor bzhag /
NK039(ti)033:348: yang gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes su zlos shig /
NK039(ti)033:351: gsol ba btab pas mdun bskyed ma mo'i mgrin par
NK039(ti)033:352: nas tshur ma dang b+h+yohyiga dmar po char ltar babs
NK039(ti)033:353: bdud rtsir 'khyil ba ngag lam du rol pas lha
NK039(ti)033:354: mo'i gsung gi dbang bskur ba thob ste /
NK039(ti)033:355: rang gi ngag ye shes kyi lha mo'i gsung du gyur /
NK039(ti)033:356: ngag gis bsags pa'i sgrib pa thams cad dag par mos /
NK039(ti)033:358: rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i snying rje'i tshig /
NK039(ti)033:359: yi ge bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho yis //
NK039(ti)033:360: skye ba med par dbang bskur ro //
NK039(ti)033:363: mgrin par bzhag hub re blud /
NK039(ti)033:366: sin tu ri'i me long gi steng na lha mo
NK039(ti)033:367: nag mo bzhugs pa dgyes bzhin du 'od du zhu
NK039(ti)033:370: rang snang ye shes kyi lha mo rang sems stong
NK039(ti)033:371: nyid gzhi rtsa dang bral bar shes pas snang srid
NK039(ti)033:372: ma mo'i stong srog la rang dbang du bsgyur te
NK039(ti)033:373: 'khor 'das thams cad sems su thag chod pa'i gdeng
NK039(ti)033:374: gis lha mo'i thugs kyi dbang bskur thob /
NK039(ti)033:375: rang sems lha mo'i thugs srog mi 'gyur ba blo
NK039(ti)033:376: bral du dbyer med par dus nam yang 'gyur ba
NK039(ti)033:380: yid mtshan ma'i rtogs pa thams cad dag par mos /
NK039(ti)033:381: don dam gnyis med byang chub sems nyid yin /
NK039(ti)033:382: rang sems rnam dag chos dbyings pho brang nas /
NK039(ti)033:383: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i ma mo ni /
NK039(ti)033:384: ma cig dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti /
NK039(ti)033:385: skye med dbyings nas 'gags med dbang bskur ro //
NK039(ti)033:387: sin d+hu ras snying khar thig le bya /
NK039(ti)033:391: dpal ldan ma mos 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal gzhoms pa dang /
NK039(ti)033:392: brtse bas bde ba'i chags pa chen po spel ba dang /
NK039(ti)033:393: dgos 'dod bsgrub pa rnams mtshon pa'i phyag mtshan rnams /
NK039(ti)033:394: gtad pas lha mo'i yon tan gyi dbang bskur ba
NK039(ti)033:395: thob ste rang la lha mo'i yon tan yongs su
NK039(ti)033:396: rdzogs yon tan gzhan don la dbang thob /
NK039(ti)033:397: rang don yid byed kyi dri ma dag par bsam la /
NK039(ti)033:398: rnam rtog 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gcod /
NK039(ti)033:399: phyag mtshan ye shes ral gri dang //
NK039(ti)033:400: sdug bsngal 'khor ba'i chags pa khrag /
NK039(ti)033:401: bde chen rol pa'i thod pa dang /
NK039(ti)033:403: rkyal pas khyed la dbang bskur ro //
NK039(ti)033:404: snang srid ma mo rgya mtsho kun //
NK039(ti)033:405: stong srog dbang du 'du bar shog /
NK039(ti)033:411: rdo rje phur bu 'di nyid phyag tu gtad pa
NK039(ti)033:412: tsam gyis lha mo'i phrin las kyi dbang bskur ba
NK039(ti)033:413: thob ste rang gis bsgrub pa'i las thams cad lha
NK039(ti)033:415: phrin las bdud bgegs dgra gdon thams cad 'dul /
NK039(ti)033:416: chos byang chub bsgrub pa la bar chod kyi dri ma thams cad dag par bsam nas /
NK039(ti)033:418: phur bu'i srung ma re m+aa ti /
NK039(ti)033:419: mthing nag mi srun gcer bu la /
NK039(ti)033:421: rno dbal bar chad bgegs la gzir /
NK039(ti)033:422: phrin las drag po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK039(ti)033:425: phur bu lag tu gtad la phyogs bcur 'dril gzhugs /
NK039(ti)033:426: spro na zan ling mdun du bkod de /
NK039(ti)033:428: bsad las zhal stabs bar du bya /
NK039(ti)033:429: de yan chad ni rdzas la brten pa dbang gi tshul du bskur ba'o //
NK039(ti)033:430: gnyis pa gtor ma la brten nas byin rlabs kyis tshul du bskur ba'i dang po /
NK039(ti)033:431: sku yi byin rlabs dbang gi slad du dmigs pa 'di bzhin zhu /
NK039(ti)033:432: spos btul nas gtor ma la 'dzugs /
NK039(ti)033:433: gtor ma 'di nyid dpal ldan lha mo drel la bcib pa'i skur gyur pa dang /
NK039(ti)033:434: khyed rang rnams kyi snying khar dpal ldan lha mo drel la bcib par mos /
NK039(ti)033:435: de gnyis kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK039(ti)033:436: nyi ma byang shar gyi mtshams nas 'dir bskyed pa
NK039(ti)033:437: dang 'dra ba'i lha mo grangs med pa byung nas
NK039(ti)033:438: / mtsho la kha ba bab pa bzhin du khyed
NK039(ti)033:439: rang gi snying ga'i lha mo la thim par bsgoms
NK039(ti)033:440: / mdzod / gu gul dkar nag dang tshil spos bsregs /
NK039(ti)033:442: rtsa sngags mang du zla zhing rol mo bya /
NK039(ti)033:443: mchod phrin 'bring po nas 'byung ba'i phyag 'tshal /
NK039(ti)033:444: b+h+yoh nag mo khrag 'thung sogs brjod mthar /
NK039(ti)033:445: gtor ma mgo thog tu bzung nas /
NK039(ti)033:446: dpal ye shes kyi lha mo nag mo chen mos
NK039(ti)033:447: rig pa 'dzin pa 'di yi lus la sku yi
NK039(ti)033:449: lus nad gdon 'byung po'i 'tshe ba las skyobs shig /
NK039(ti)033:450: ces gsol ba btab pas gtor ma'i lha mo'i dpral
NK039(ti)033:451: ba nas dkar po char ltar babs te byung khyed
NK039(ti)033:452: rang gi dpral bar thim pas lus lha yi nus
NK039(ti)033:453: pa rdzogs pa'i mos pa mdzod //
NK039(ti)033:454: rtsa sngags bzla zhing spos rol bya /
NK039(ti)033:455: gnyis pa gsung gi dbang bskur ba la 'dun pa 'di bzhin mdzod //
NK039(ti)033:456: gtor ma de mgrin par bzung la /
NK039(ti)033:458: ngag la gsung gi byin gyis rlobs shig /
NK039(ti)033:459: ngag las sgrib bag chags las skyobs shig ces gsol btab pas /
NK039(ti)033:460: gtor ma 'di dang tha mi dad pa'i dpal ldan lha mo dpag tu med pa dang /
NK039(ti)033:461: tsa ba'i dpal lha mo'i mgrin pa nas +aahyiga dmar po char ltar babs /
NK039(ti)033:462: khyed rang gi mgrin par thim pas ngag sngags kyi nus pa dang ldan par mos shig /
NK039(ti)033:463: rtsa sngags bzla zhing spos rol bya /
NK039(ti)033:464: zhar byung ma ltar bsten pa'i bzlas lung blang ba la /
NK039(ti)033:465: lha mo'i thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' koo ri
NK039(ti)033:466: ma sngon mo g.yas zhing dbyug g.yon thod khrag bsnams
NK039(ti)033:467: pa'i thugs kar zla ba'i steng du ral gri'i so
NK039(ti)033:468: yu'i mtshams su ma nag mo la rtsa sngags /
NK039(ti)033:469: srog snying dang bcas pas bskor ba las gnyis pa zhig thugs ka'i nu 'bur nas tshur la byung /
NK039(ti)033:470: khyod rang gi snying khar thim par gyur pa'i mos pas sngags 'di rnams rjes zlos lan gsum zhu /
NK039(ti)033:472: rtsa sngags gtso 'khor gyi srog snying rnams bzlar 'jug /
NK039(ti)033:473: gsum pa thugs kyi dbang bskur ba la 'dun pa 'di bzhin mdzod /
NK039(ti)033:474: yang gtor ma snying gar bzung la /
NK039(ti)033:476: yid la thugs kyi byin gyis rlobs shig /
NK039(ti)033:477: yid sdig pa dang dri ma las skyobs shig /
NK039(ti)033:478: ces gsol ba btab pas gtor ma dang gcig pa'i
NK039(ti)033:479: lha mo'i snying ga nas lha mo grangs med pa
NK039(ti)033:480: dang / khyad par du mahsngo skya las 'od zer sna tshogs grangs med pa gcig byung /
NK039(ti)033:481: thugs ka'i h'u la thim pas thugs gnyis su med pa rtogs pa'i nus pa dang ldan par bsgoms /
NK039(ti)033:482: nas rtsa sngags bzla zhing spos rol bya /
NK039(ti)033:483: bzhi pa yon tan phrin las gnyis ka'i byin rlabs
NK039(ti)033:484: gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba'i slad du dmigs pa 'di
NK039(ti)033:485: bzhin mdzod / gtor ma lag tu gtad nas /
NK039(ti)033:487: skal ldan 'di dag gi rgyud la yon tan dang phrin las kyi byin gyis rlobs shig /
NK039(ti)033:488: sa dang lam gyi yon tan ma lus pa rdzogs
NK039(ti)033:489: nas phrin las rnam pa bzhi 'grub par mdzad du
NK039(ti)033:490: gsol / ces gsol ba btab pas lha mo'i lte ba nas 'od zer ser po dang /
NK039(ti)033:491: gsang gnas nas 'od zer ljang gu grangs med pa
NK039(ti)033:492: byung khyed rnams kyi lte ba dang gsang bar thim
NK039(ti)033:493: par bsgom shig // gsang ba dur khrod dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)033:494: khams gsum gdul ba za byed chen mo ste //
NK039(ti)033:495: rdo rje d+r+wa ba dang ni glog 'gyu ma //
NK039(ti)033:496: ru lu ru lu'i sgra skad drag po yis //
NK039(ti)033:497: raka mo kro d+ha k+sha yis bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)033:498: yun gyi dpal dang mgon du khyed bsten na //
NK039(ti)033:499: myur du dngos grub stsal gcig dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)033:500: ru ru sogs rtsa sngags bzla zhing spos rol bya /
NK039(ti)033:501: slob ma brgyud 'dzin 'dra yin na gtor ma'i lha de la bstim /
NK039(ti)033:502: gzhan slob dpon gyi thugs dkar bstim /
NK039(ti)033:503: gtor zan ma mo'i dngos grub tu bsam nas gsol gcig /
NK039(ti)033:505: de ltar dbang bskur ba'i don rang sems don gyi
NK039(ti)033:506: dpal ldan lha mo'i thugs ye shes ni rdo rje
NK039(ti)033:508: spros pa yod med gang yin min sogs nye bar zhi ba /
NK039(ti)033:509: dpe dang tshig gis mi mtshon pa so sor rang
NK039(ti)033:510: gi rig pa rnam kun mchog ldan gyi rang bzhin
NK039(ti)033:511: sgyu ma lta bu'i rig stong zung du 'jug pa
NK039(ti)033:512: ni skye med don gyi dpal lha mo ste /
NK039(ti)033:513: de rnams lus gnad rang bab tu lhod bag rang zhir chug /
NK039(ti)033:514: sems 'das ma 'ongs yid byed da lta'i rtog pa rang zhir zhog la /
NK039(ti)033:515: dgag sgrub blo yis ngang thad kar lhod de bskyangs bar bya dgos pas de'ang /
NK039(ti)033:517: bsam du med do sems nyid nam mkha' che /
NK039(ti)033:518: sems nyid ma dper tshig chad yod pa kun dang bral /
NK039(ti)033:519: zhes gsungs pa ltar ngang bskyangs ba la brtson par zhu /
NK039(ti)033:520: tshul 'adi'ang spu gri ya ma'i rgyud las /
NK039(ti)033:521: gsang ba'i dbang bskur thob pa ni //
NK039(ti)033:522: ma nor snang ba rang gi sems //
NK039(ti)033:523: sems nyid ma bcos thig le'i ngang //
NK039(ti)033:524: sems la rang dbang thob pa na //
NK039(ti)033:525: chos kyi sku yi rang bzhin te //
NK039(ti)033:526: khams gsum 'khor ba'i g.yul las rgyal //
NK039(ti)033:528: de dag gis ni ye shes pa ltar dbang bskur ba'i rim pa grub bo //
NK039(ti)033:529: gnyis pa 'jig rten pa ltar rjes su gnang ba bka' gtad kyi don du man+dala phul /
NK039(ti)033:530: gsol ba 'debs pa 'di yi rjes zlos mdzod /
NK039(ti)033:531: sh+aakya seng ge'i bstan bsrung ma /
NK039(ti)033:532: ma mo yongs kyi gtso mo mchog /
NK039(ti)033:533: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo yi //
NK039(ti)033:534: rjes su gnang ba stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)033:535: lan gsum 'jig rten pa'i ma mo la rten bskyed mi dgos gsungs /
NK039(ti)033:536: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od zer lcags kyu lta
NK039(ti)033:537: bu 'phros pa'i nyi ma byang shar gyi mtshams thod
NK039(ti)033:538: pa'i sku mkhar nas dpal lha mo nag mo ma
NK039(ti)033:539: mo bye ba 'bum sde'i bka' 'khor dang bcas skad
NK039(ti)033:540: cig gi glog 'khyugs pa ltar spyan drangs nas rten
NK039(ti)033:541: gtor la thim par bsam nas rtsa sngags bco lnga
NK039(ti)033:543: 'bul ba'i gtor ma byin rlabs bya /
NK039(ti)033:544: dam bsre ba'i phyir nang mchod nas hub gcig slob bu la byin nas /
NK039(ti)033:545: deng phyin chad khyed kyis dpal lha mo nag mo
NK039(ti)033:546: bsnyen bsgrub las gsum gyi sgo nas rgyun du brten
NK039(ti)033:547: cing gsang sngags kyi rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NK039(ti)033:549: bye brag dus kyi gtor ma dang bsgrub brten bskang ba'i rdzas dang rdo sol chu mi bskyur /
NK039(ti)033:550: bya nag dang khyi nag la rdo mi brdeg /
NK039(ti)033:551: 'tshubs ma la mos mgar yug mi brten /
NK039(ti)033:553: 'khrugs skang bya ba la sogs pa dam tshig mtha'
NK039(ti)033:554: dag tshul bzhin bsgrub pa la brtson par byos shig
NK039(ti)033:555: / slob mas kyang khas blang ba 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK039(ti)033:556: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig 'di //
NK039(ti)033:557: gsung ba gsum gyi dbyings nas byung //
NK039(ti)033:559: grub na 'jig pa'i dus med pas //
NK039(ti)033:560: dam tshig rnams las bdag mi 'da' //
NK039(ti)033:561: badz+ra sa ma ya na ra kan /
NK039(ti)033:564: slob ma dam pa khyed kyis dengs phyin chad dpal
NK039(ti)033:565: ldan ma'i bsnyen bsgrub las gsum 'di dag su la
NK039(ti)033:566: yang gsang bar dam nos shig /
NK039(ti)033:567: ces brjod pas bdud rtsi thig gcig lte thog tu gtor /
NK039(ti)033:568: de nas nang mchod hub cha gcig rten gtor la 'bul nas /
NK039(ti)033:570: khyed dang slob bu dam basre'o //
NK039(ti)033:571: zhes sbyar dam bsgrags pa'i skabs /
NK039(ti)033:572: dam tshig dang ldan pa 'di dag la /
NK039(ti)033:574: gsang ba'i dam tshig gi rgya bstan /
NK039(ti)033:575: mchod phrin chen mo'i gzhung nas 'byung ba'i sman raka gtor gsum 'bul /
NK039(ti)033:577: b+h+yoh dbyings phyug dpal ldan mas bstod /
NK039(ti)033:578: de nas sring dang grogs dang bran ltar bsten pa'i
NK039(ti)033:579: zlas lung blang ba la dmigs pa 'di bzhin du
NK039(ti)033:580: mdzod / mchod phrin chen mo'i bsnyen skabs kyi /
NK039(ti)033:582: khyed rang gi zhes bsgyur nas sngags gsum po re re nas gsum gsum bzlar gzhug /
NK039(ti)033:583: slob bu thun min brgyud pa 'dzin nges la srog
NK039(ti)033:584: gi las brgyad kyi dmigs gnad rgyud nas 'byung ba
NK039(ti)033:585: ltar 'bog / rten gtor spos bcas lag tu gtad nas /
NK039(ti)033:586: dpal lha mo nag mo rang byung gi rgyal mo /
NK039(ti)033:587: skems ma chu srin mgo can ma bdun /
NK039(ti)033:591: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK039(ti)033:593: bdud mo bye ba 'bum ste bka' 'khor dang bcas
NK039(ti)033:594: pas dpal chen po'i spyan sngar khas blangs shing dam
NK039(ti)033:596: dam ldan rdo rje'i slob bu thun min yin na 'di zhes bya ba'i zhes ming brjod /
NK039(ti)033:598: 'di rnams kyis rtsi byin pa'i zas zo /
NK039(ti)033:600: lus dang grib ma bzhin du 'grogs /
NK039(ti)033:601: sdang bar byed pa'i dgra thul /
NK039(ti)033:602: bar du gcod pa'i rkyen bzlog /
NK039(ti)033:603: slob dpon thun mong min pa la /
NK039(ti)033:604: sku bstan cing rtogs pa'i grogs su mdzod la nyams dang rtogs pa spor /
NK039(ti)033:606: dam tshig gi bya ra mdzod /
NK039(ti)033:607: dus 'di nas byang chub kyi bar du 'bral ba
NK039(ti)033:608: med par mdzod cig ces gsol ba dpal ldan lha
NK039(ti)033:609: mos kyang / bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bka'
NK039(ti)033:610: yi bsgo ba bzhin rigs kyi bu khyed kyi 'gal
NK039(ti)033:611: rkyen bar chad thams cad ngas sel /
NK039(ti)033:612: mthun rkyen dge ba thams cad ngas bsgrub ces gsung lhang lhang byon par mos /
NK039(ti)033:613: gtor ma'i stod nas cha gcig lha mo la 'bul /
NK039(ti)033:614: smad de dngos grub tu mos la dpon slob kun nas cung zad rol /
NK039(ti)033:615: de nas brgyud pa 'dzin nges kyi slob bu thun min la bla rdo dang srog 'khor sbyin nas /
NK039(ti)033:616: rigs kyi bu khyed kyis dpal lha mo nag mo'i
NK039(ti)033:617: bla rdo dang srog gi 'khor lo 'di nyid mi
NK039(ti)033:618: 'bral bar lus dang grib ma bzhin 'changs shig /
NK039(ti)033:619: skal ba dang ldan pa khyed cag gi ma mo'i dam tshig gi rim pa thub par mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)033:620: dngos grub thob par gyis la sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrungs shig /
NK039(ti)033:621: de phyin chad dpal ldan ma'i bsnyen bsgrub las gsum gyis shig /
NK039(ti)033:624: lha tshogs thams cad rjes la bsdu gshegs gang yang mi dgos gsungs so //
NK039(ti)033:625: slob mas kyang ji skad gsungs pa ltar 'dzin par bgyi 'o snyams pas 'di'i rjes zlos zhu /
NK039(ti)033:627: 'dir dpon slob gnyis kas gtor ma gsar du bshams mchod gsol rgyas par bya'o //
NK039(ti)033:630: lus longs spyod 'bul ba rnams spyi ltar bya'o //
NK039(ti)033:631: de ni ma gsol rgyun du brten cing chos brgyud 'di la gus ngos rnams la bya'o //
NK039(ti)033:632: gnyis pa de la thun mong gi dmigs rim spyi dbang rjes bya tshul las /
NK039(ti)033:633: ye shes dbab pa'i bar gang bzhin /
NK039(ti)033:635: slob dpon rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs ka nas lcags kyu lta bu'i 'od zer 'phros /
NK039(ti)033:636: nyi ma byang shar gyi mtshams /
NK039(ti)033:637: mtsho mu le mthing gi gzhal yas /
NK039(ti)033:639: dpal ldan lha mo ye shes pa spyan drangs te
NK039(ti)033:640: skad cig gis khyed rang gi snying gar sib kyis
NK039(ti)033:641: thim / snying nang du ye shes sems dpa' lha
NK039(ti)033:642: mo dre'u la bcib pa zhig la thim par bsgoms
NK039(ti)033:646: dbyings phyug dpal ldan mas bstod /
NK039(ti)033:647: rdzas la rten nas dbang yongs rdzogs bskur rten gtor lag tu gtad la /
NK039(ti)033:649: dam tshig khas blangs nas 'jug ste rdzogs par byas pas kyang /
NK039(ti)033:650: gsol ka btang ba'i grogs bcol ba sogs pa'i snod du rung ba tsam mo //
NK039(ti)033:651: de ltar na de dag gis grub pa'i slob dpon chen po d+ha na sang+k+ri ta yi lugs /
NK039(ti)033:652: slob dpon chen po'i bka' srog las byon pa'i bstan
NK039(ti)033:653: srung gi rgyal mo rdo rje re m+aa ti'i ye
NK039(ti)033:655: 'jig rten pa ltar rjes su gnang ba /
NK039(ti)033:656: rgyal ba kahthoga pa'i bstan srung gi gtso mo /
NK039(ti)033:657: thugs gtsigs tu mdzad pa legs par phul grub pa lags /
NK039(ti)033:658: mthar dge ba bsngosa la rang gnas su btang ngo //
NK039(ti)033:660: slar yang slob dpon gyis bskang bshags dang /
NK039(ti)033:661: gtor ma la 'gugs gzhugs byas te /
NK039(ti)033:662: rjes chog gi rim pa bya'o //
NK039(ti)033:663: 'di ni srid pa ma mo'i yum gtso mo mu
NK039(ti)033:664: kha le'i thugs las sprul pa'i lha mo rang byung
NK039(ti)033:666: shin tu gnyan cing zab pas su thod thod la spel bar mi bya'o //
NK039(ti)033:667: gang gi srog dbang gi shin tu zab pa la /
NK039(ti)033:668: sngon du bsnyen pa 'grub dgos shing /
NK039(ti)033:669: khyad par tshogs dang gtor ma mang du phul nas bya dgos gsungs so //
NK039(ti)033:670: bslu med rig 'dzin rgyud pa'i zhal lung chab //
NK039(ti)033:671: man ngag yi ger rnying nas dus ring mos //
NK039(ti)033:672: 'das kyang byin rlabs drod chen ma //
NK039(ti)033:673: snying la snyan brgyud bdud rtsi cir yang 'khol //
NK039(ti)033:674: 'dir 'bad gsang ba sgrogs pa'i nyes skyon gang //
NK039(ti)033:675: bla ma mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la bzod gsol zhing //
NK039(ti)033:676: 'di dgos tshe rabs kun tu lha mo yis //
NK039(ti)033:677: byang chub lam gyi srung mar 'bral med shog /
NK039(ti)033:678: ces pa'ang yum chen mkha' 'gro'i brdas bskul te /
NK039(ti)033:679: gangs can grub gnas thams cad kyi rgyal mo /
NK039(ti)033:680: shar kahthoga rdo rje'i gdan gyi ri bo'i spor /
NK039(ti)033:681: bstan 'gror lhag bsam rab dkar zla ba'i lang tshos snying la bde ba yin pa /
NK039(ti)033:682: mang thos snyan brgyud 'dzin pa'i dge slong rig pa
NK039(ti)033:683: 'dzin pa si tu chos kyi rgya mtshos bgyis pa
